of these Hollywood super-hunks.

116
00:07:20,626 --> 00:07:24,616
We need a dumpy,
unappealing loser: an everyman.

117
00:07:26,077 --> 00:07:28,510
Can you help me out?
I need change for a dollar.

118
00:07:28,635 --> 00:07:30,032
I also need a dollar.

119
00:07:38,506 --> 00:07:41,001
You... are... acceptable.

120
00:07:41,169 --> 00:07:42,795
