No kidding?!

132
00:08:19,952 --> 00:08:21,369
Homer, we have a problem.

133
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:24,706
Fine. I'll give back the Oscars
I stole from the lobby.

134
00:08:25,215 --> 00:08:28,259
- Do you want the Golden Globe?
- No! No...

135
00:08:28,384 --> 00:08:29,961
